{"tid":688423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田北辰：港鐵需考慮是否拆卸紅磡站檢查","createTime":"2018-06-03T08:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T08:26:17.000Z","uid":37554,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f75750b7800e097ccb4be938534c49311c035cd0","tid":688423,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:08:28.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】港鐵沙中綫紅磡站月台鋼筋接駁位造假事件，立法會鐵路事宜小組主席田北辰認為，現時首要是查清楚負責工程的分判商是否存心欺瞞，而港鐵及總承建商禮頓是否知情不報。他又指，港鐵要考慮如何確保站內結構安全，包括是否需要拆卸檢查。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰又認為，政府應成立獨立調查委員會調查事件，弄清楚事件是否涉及造假，以及月台結構是否安全。"},{"pid":"4f9e4490204a232975b999d6bb7f639a1b89980c","tid":688423,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:14:56.000Z","msg":"正苦同民賤聯睬你都on9"},{"pid":"cbe29ef795c8e750f1f7863c8f05378475865293","tid":688423,"uid":73043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"有得唔拆咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe4d6e111a50eee3b923f022e171b918ad7efb6","tid":688423,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:15:36.000Z","msg":"GDP GO GO GO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbc7da7eadd45ae0cfa066ace83c0031ca99e10","tid":688423,"uid":42187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cbe29ef795c8e750f1f7863c8f05378475865293","tid":688423,"uid":73043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"有得唔拆咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"支那辰：我話ok就ok"},{"pid":"eb0a15eef3b940ddf13d94fde36987886bdaca55","tid":688423,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbe29ef795c8e750f1f7863c8f05378475865293","tid":688423,"uid":73043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"有得唔拆咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi